
 README file for Apache::NNTPGateway
 ===================================

 A NNTP (Usenet newsgroups) interface for mod_perl enabled Apache web server.

 * Install this module somewhere in your @INC path.

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

 * Read the documentation in the source or man (or perldoc)
   Apache::NNTPGateway once installed.

 * Report bugs to author: heddy Boubaker <boubaker@cpan.org>



